org.iotivity.base

Class OcResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.iotivity.base.OcResource

  • public class OcResource
extends java.lang.Object
    OcResource represents an OC resource. A resource could be a light controller, temperature sensor, smoke detector, etc. A resource comes with a well-defined contract or interface onto which you can perform different operations, such as turning on the light, getting the current temperature or subscribing for event notifications from the smoke detector. A resource can be composed of one or more resources.
